<H3> <TI>   Defense Minister Sees Cooperation With Russia as Main Issue </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0201215194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1930 GMT 
2 Jan 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD0201215194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Radio Slavyanka" program of the Russian Defense </F>
Ministry] 
  [Text] The main issue for Kazakhstan in the military sphere 
is close military cooperation with the Russian Federation, 
according to an address by Kazakhstani Defense Minister Sagadat 
Nurmagambetov to the military department collegium. We quote 
from KAZAKHSTAN SARBAZY -- WARRIOR OF KAZAKHSTAN. Realistic 
conditions for such cooperation do exist, the minister stressed. 
The legal basis for this is the document on friendship and 
cooperation between Kazakhstan and Russia. 

</TEXT>

