<H3> <TI>   Ministry Reports Abkhazian Attack on Zugdidi </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3112131193 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1113 GMT 31 Dec 93 </F>
<F P=103> LD3112131193 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow INTERFAX </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Abkhazian troops attacked the village of Ganmukhuri, 
Zugdidi District, officials of the Georgian Interior Ministry 
told Interfax. 
  The Georgian units held the enemy back. There are no reports 
of casualties. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

