<F P=100> Georgia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Ministry Denies Buildup of Troops in Tbilisi </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3012155893 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel 
Network in Russian 1500 GMT 30 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD3012155893 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel 
Network </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A representative of Georgia's Defense Ministry 
called reports that forces are being concentrated in military 
camps around Tbilisi blatant disinformation designed to 
discredit the Defense Ministry. The Security Ministry also 
denied reports that the main bulk of its forces were being 
concentrated in Tbilisi. The Security Ministry is not ready to 
comment on the incidents in Tbilisi on 24 and 25 December before 
the state commission investigating them, headed by Prime 
Minister Patsatsia, has finished its work. 

</TEXT>

