<H3> <TI>   Chernomyrdin Appoints TASS Deputy Director Generals </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3112131893 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1314 GMT 31 Dec 93 </F>
<F P=103> LD3112131893 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Moscow December 31 -- On Friday [31 December], 
Russian Federation Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin appointed 
Yuriy Sizov and Yuriy Subbotin as deputy directors-general of 
ITAR-TASS, the official information and telegraph agency of 
Russia. 
  The appointments were made in accordance with President 
Yeltsin's recent decree on ITAR-TASS. 

</TEXT>

