<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Russian Federation Defense Ministry Information </F>
and Press Directorate: "Not Removed from Duties"] 
  [Text] The report carried by certain mass media that 
Lieutenant General Yuriy Konovalenko, commander of the Russian 
military unit temporarily stationed on the territory of the 
former Semipalatinsk test range, has been removed from his post 
does not accord with the facts. 
  As a Russian citizen and serviceman of the Russian Armed 
Forces he cannot be removed from his post by decision of another 
country's leadership. 
  Yu. Konovalenko is currently on leave. 

