<F P=102>  LD0301131694 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 1200 GMT 3 
Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0301131694 </F>
<F P=104>  Riga Radio Riga Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Latvian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Danish Defense Minister Hans Haekkerup arrived in 
Latvia today, for an official working visit. The minister is 
accompanied by Andres Strodbach, state secretary at the Danish 
Ministry of Defense, Per Samsten, head of the ministry's foreign 
relations department, and other officials. 
  The Danish delegation has already met Latvia's Defense 
Minister Valdis Pavlovskis. Later today the Danish and Latvian 
ministers of defense will sign a military cooperation agreement. 
The Danish official also plans to meet Dainis Turlais, 
commander of the defense forces. The guests will be acquainted 
with problems facing the Latvian defense forces, and informed 
about the course of the Russian Army withdrawal, Latvia's wish 
to integrate into Europe and NATO, and possible Danish 
assistance with materials and equipment. 
  The Danish delegation will also meet Prime Minister Valdis 
Birkavs. 

