<H3> <TI>   Parliament Vetoes Presidential Edict on Company </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0301204794 Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY in Ukrainian 30 Dec 93 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> AU0301204794 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Ukraine's Supreme Council Decree on the Ukrainian </F>
Presidential Edict of 13 August 1993 `On Creating the 
Joint-Stock Ship Building Concern `Blasco' -- the `Black Sea 
Steamship Company''" issued in Kiev on 24 Dec 93] 
