<F P=102>  AU0501112794 Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY in Ukrainian 4 Jan 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> AU0501112794 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Negotiations Between Ukraine and </F>
Azerbaijan"] 
  [Text] On the eve of the New Year, governmental 
delegations of Ukraine and Azerbaijan held negotiations in Kiev. 
They discussed an extensive circle of problems concerning the 
development and intensification of the interaction between the 
two countries in the economic, financial, and other spheres. 
  An agreement was signed on trade and economic cooperation 
for 
1994 and an accord was reached on holding negotiations at the 
level of presidents and parliamentarians at the beginning of 
1994 for the purpose of further development of interstate 
relations. 
  The Ukrainian delegation was headed by Vice Prime Minister 
V. 
Shmarov and the Azerbaijani one by L. Abbasov, first deputy 
prime minister. 

