<H3> <TI>   More Officials Dismissed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0501101394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0940 GMT 5 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0501101394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Moscow, January 5 (TASS) -- The Russian Government 
dismissed Pyotr Chernomord from the post of deputy finance 
minister in connection "with a transfer to another job". 
  Aleksandr Aleshin was dismissed from the post of the first 
deputy communication minister "at his request". 
  The government decided to institute yet another post of 
first 
deputy social security minister and Lyudmila Bezlepkina was 
appointed to occupy it. 

</TEXT>

