<H3> <TI>   State Duma To Form 17 Committees </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0401214994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 2126 GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0401214994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspsondent] </F>
  [Text] Moscow January 5 TASS -- A joint meeting of the 
Organizational Center for Preparations of the First Meetings of 
the Russian Federal Assembly chambers and the Commission on 
Formation of State Duma Commissions was held on Tuesday in 
Kremlin's Oval Hall, the Russian Federal Assembly's press 
service reports. 
  The meeting discussed aspects of formation of State Duma 
committees and commissions. 
  The deputies concluded the State Duma shall form 17 
committees to include: 
  1. The committee of constitutional legislation, legal reform 
and human rights; 
  2. The committee on public associations and religious 
organizations; 
  3. Committee on labor and social protection; 
  4. Committee on health care and ecology; 
  5. Committee on education, culture and science; 
  6. Committee on affairs of women, children and family; 
  7. Committee on budget and taxes; 
  8. Committee on economic reform, property and 
privatization; 
  9. Committee on banks, credits and money circulation; 
  10. Committee on agrarian issues; 
  11. Committee on industry, power engineering, transport 
and communications; 
  12. Committee on natural resources and ecology; 
  13. Committee on defence; 
  14. Committee on international affairs; 
  15. Committee on security; 
  16. Committee on affairs of the federation, national and 
regional policy, local government; 
  17. Committee on organization of work of the state duma. 
  The work of the Commission on Formation of State Duma 
Commissions will continue on January 5. 

</TEXT>

